{"id":2307,"date":"2025-10-14T01:34:38","date_gmt":"2025-10-14T01:34:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/?page_id=2307"},"modified":"2025-12-03T12:41:22","modified_gmt":"2025-12-03T12:41:22","slug":"npack-factory","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/about-us\/npack-factory","title":{"rendered":"Npack Factory"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"2307\" class=\"elementor elementor-2307\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b9d536 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4b9d536\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acaf631 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"acaf631\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShanghai Npack adheres to international standards, ensuring high quality and reliability. Rigorous manufacturing and quality control meet or exceed customer expectations. A 2,600 sqm factory with advanced equipment supports scalable, precise production for global needs. This capacity reinforces their ability to deliver consistent results worldwide.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20b5fe3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"20b5fe3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b7b3ed e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8b7b3ed\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f276830 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f276830\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4052e27 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4052e27\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6e7de0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d6e7de0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Liquid Bottling Equipments Manufacturer<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2052fe8 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2052fe8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01f4660 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"01f4660\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Shanghai Npack is a liquid bottling equipment manufacturer, verified by SGS every year. Our factory floor space is 2600 (\u33a1). We are a manufacturer with the following verified capabilities:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a69a78c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a69a78c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>International service centers: we provide local after-sales services in specific countries.<\/li><li>Full customization: we supply customization based on specific requirement descriptions.<\/li><li>Sample-based customization: Npack supports customization based on samples.<\/li><li>Design-based customization: Npack supports customization based on design drawings.<\/li><li>Minor customization: Minor customization refers to custom logos, packaging, or graphics.<\/li><li>Raw-material traceability identification: Npack supports buyers in quality traceability.<\/li><li>Finished product inspection: Npack conducts stringent inspections on all its finished products.<\/li><li>QA\/QC inspectors: Number of supplier\u2019s QA\/QC inspection employees.<\/li><li>On-site material inspection: The supplier has a relevant inspection process for this product\u2019s raw materials.<\/li><li>Quality traceability: Supports buyers in quality traceability.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a52705b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a52705b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67bc7c5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"67bc7c5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad3e20d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ad3e20d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Npack Factory Gallary<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-949782b elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"949782b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91dea95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"91dea95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Shanghai Npack strictly adheres to international standards and best practices, highlighting its unwavering commitment to excellence and reliability across all its operations. This dedication to quality is evident in every aspect of their work, from the meticulous attention to detail in their manufacturing processes to the rigorous quality control measures they implement. By following globally recognized standards, Shanghai Npack ensures that their products consistently meet or exceed customer expectations, thereby reinforcing their reputation as a trusted and dependable partner in the industry.<\/p><p>Additionally, Shanghai Npack\u2019s impressive factory footprint is a testament to its robust manufacturing capabilities and operational scale. With a vast floor space of 2,600 square meters, the facility is designed to accommodate large-scale productions efficiently. This substantial size not only underscores the company\u2019s ability to produce a wide range of products but also demonstrates its readiness to meet the diverse and evolving needs of its global clientele.<\/p><p>The expansive factory space is equipped with state-of-the-art machinery and advanced technology, enabling Shanghai Npack to maintain high productivity levels while ensuring precision and quality in every product they manufacture. This extensive capacity allows the company to handle significant production volumes, catering to various industries and markets around the world.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8e50bd e-con-